{{Han compound|相|心|t1=to look at|t2=heart, mind|ls=psc|c1=p|c2=s}} – to think, to consider.

===Etymology===
From {{och-l|相|to observe; appearance}} (“appearance > to visualise > to think”).

Cognate to {{cog|sit-jap|sɯso|t=to think}} and {{cog|sit-sit|kasəsō|ka-səsō|t=to think}} ({{zh-ref|Zhang, Jacques and Lai 2019 p. 84}}); from this, one can reconstruct {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*saŋ|t=to think}}.

